    <mxCell id="100" value="app/ml_adapter/pipeline_wrapper.py  —  ML Boundary&#xa;SOLE FILE THAT IMPORTS FROM src/  |  Adds src/ to sys.path at startup  |  Loads nnU-Net segmentation model + ResNet3D EF model once into RAM&#xa;run_full_pipeline(path_4ch, path_2ch, output_dir, on_stage_update)  →  { measurements: {...}, visualizations: {filenames} }&#xa;Copies outputs/ → jobs/{job_id}/outputs/ after each run  |  Calls on_stage_update(stage, pct) at each pipeline stage"
      style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fef3c7;strokeColor=#d97706;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=9;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;"
      vertex="1" parent="1">
